{"tid":942310,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求醫生巴打神仙下凡打救小弟外婆。。。。","createTime":"2018-12-15T15:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T14:58:12.000Z","uid":9506,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33b7c47b043d103ede29b6227c528572155fc7f7","tid":942310,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟住喺廈門嘅外婆聽聞食左7,8年精神藥物（好似係醫depression），其中包括Levodopa/Benserazide Hydrochloride、Pramipexole Dihydrochloride Sustained Release Tablets、Trazodone Hydrochloride以及Venlafaxine。直到最近身體開始出現一D問題，其中最嚴重既係條tongue會無法控制地伸出伸入，同埋手腳協調同活動差左。<br />\n<br />\n小弟岩先係網上查左陣，覺得最有可能既原因應該係Tardive Dyskinesia，咁岩上年香港又入口左美國FDA最新批准治療TD既藥物INGREZZA(valbenazine)，所以想叫外婆落黎睇下私家醫院（港安或者養和）。<br />\n<br />\n不過由於小弟都唔係醫生，所以想各位連登神醫畀ｄ意見小弟，或者可唔可以介紹番相關可靠有料既精神科醫生畀小弟出去consult下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc339468c5d49e380c767dbc929b4bd4eacc127","tid":942310,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"見你咁孝順幫你推下<br />\n但做咩要開三個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060839435d1f3c1aab2a1802ffb0a59726489291","tid":942310,"uid":9506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc339468c5d49e380c767dbc929b4bd4eacc127","tid":942310,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"見你咁孝順幫你推下<br />\n但做咩要開三個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"平時我都唔會咁，今次事關重大，唯有出此下策以增加曝光率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af198028d9deb813c9391719c758428130c1163a","tid":942310,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"060839435d1f3c1aab2a1802ffb0a59726489291","tid":942310,"uid":9506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":